@node "GuiX_Checksum" "5.5.1 GuiX:  Checksum calculator"


 @{b}Short key: @{fg shine}RAMIGA + 1@{ub}@{fg text}

 E' un tool per il calcolo multialgoritmo della checksum dei file-disks. Gli
algoritmi disponibili sono:

 Brick CRC-32  <-- Deriva dal comando GNU Brick
 BSD           <-- Senza tabella del polinomio
 MD5           <-- 64 bit con tabella del polinomio
 Posix         <-- Con tabella del polinomio
 System V      <-- Senza tabella del polinomio


  @{fg fill}+-+-------------------------+-+-+@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg text}*@{fg fill}|@{fg text} CheckSum Calculator     @{fg fill}|@{fg text}%@{fg fill}|@{fg text}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}+-+-------------------------+-+-+@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-----------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}       +----------------++-+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}  File |                ||@{fg shine}^@{fg text}| @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Nome del file per il calcolo
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}       +----------------++-+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}       +--+----------------+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{u}@{fg text}M@{uu}ethod ||^|  Brick CRC-32  | @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Metodo utilizzato
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}       +--+----------------+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-----------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+---------- Checksum ---------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text} Dec @{fg shine}-@{fg text}                       @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Risultato decimale
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text} Hex @{fg shine}-@{fg text}                       @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Risultato esadecimale
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-----------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-----------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}+----------+    +----------+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}|   C@{u}a@{uu}lc   |    |  @{u}C@{uu}ancel  | @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Bottoni di controllo:
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}+----------+    +----------+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}     Calc   = calcola
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-----------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}     Cancel = chiude la finestra
  @{fg fill}+-----------------------------+-+@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|                             |@{fg text}/@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}+-----------------------------+-+@{fg text}

  Funzioni attivabili da menů:

  @{b}Checksum@{ub}
    Calculate   <-- Attiva il calcolo (short key @{fg shine}RAMIGA + C@{fg text})
    ---------
    Close       <-- Chiude la finestra (short key @{fg shine}RAMIGA + Q@{fg text})
@endnode

@node "GuiX_DizToolkit" "5.5.2 GuiX: Diz Toolkit"


 @{b}Short Key:@{ub} @{fg shine}RAMIGA + 2@{fg text}

 Il Diz Toolkit serve per aggiungere, estrarre e rimuovere commenti (diz)  a
file-disks  comppressi  con  algoritmi XPK. Dal punto di vista tecnico, alla
fine del file compresso viene  aggiunto  un  file  di  testo  opportunamente
delimitato da stringhe.



 +---- Nome del file
 |
 |
 |   @{fg fill}+-+-----------------------------------+-+-+@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg text}*@{fg fill}|@{fg text} Diz Toolkit                       @{fg fill}|@{fg text}%@{fg fill}|@{fg text}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}+-+-----------------------------------+-+-+@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+--------File-Disk--------+ +-----------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}+--------------------++-+@{fg shine}| |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 +-> @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}|Ram:MyDisk.xfx      ||@{fg shine}^@{fg text}|@{fg shine}| |@{fg text}|   @{u}N@{uu}ew   |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- @{"Aggiunge un commento" link "GuiX_DizToolkit_New" 0}
     @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}+--------------------++-+@{fg shine}| |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
     |@{fg shine}+-------------------------+ |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
     |@{fg shine}+-------FILE-ID.diz-------+ |@{fg text}| @{u}E@{uu}xtract |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Estrae il commento
     @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|+---------------------+-+| |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
     |@{fg shine}||@{b}@{fg text}FileType:@{ub}@{fg shine}            |@{fg text}*@{fg shine}|| |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
     |@{fg shine}||@{fg text}[NUKE] File-Disk@{fg shine}     | || |@{fg text}| @{u}R@{uu}emove  |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Rimuove il commento
     @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}||@{b}@{fg text}Name:@{ub}@{fg shine}                | || |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 +-> @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}||@{fg text}My Disk@{fg shine}              +-+| |           |@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}||@{b}@{fg text}Author:@{ub}@{fg shine}              |@{fg text}=@{fg shine}|| |           |@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}||@{fg text}Alessandro Pedretti@{fg shine}  +-+| |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}||@{b}@{fg text}Generated by:@{ub}@{fg shine}        |@{fg text}=@{fg shine}|| |@{fg text}|  @{u}C@{uu}lose  |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Chiude la finestra
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|+---------------------+-+| |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-------------------------+ +-----------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}+---------------------------------------+-+@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|                                       |@{fg text}/@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}+---------------------------------------+-+@{fg text}
 |
 |
 +---- Descrizione del commento


 Funzioni attivabili da menů:

 @{b}Diz Toolkit@{ub}
   Close      <--- Chiude la fiestra (short key @{fg shine}RAMIGA + C@{fg text}).
@endnode

@node "GuiX_DizToolkit_New" "5.5.4.1 GuiX: Nuovo Diz"


 La seguente finestra permette di inserire i campi del commento:


 @{fg fill}+-+---------------------------------+-+-+
 |@{fg text}*@{fg fill}|@{fg text} New Diz                         @{fg fill}|@{fg text}%@{fg fill}|@{fg text}|@{fg fill}|
 +-+---------------------------------+-+-+
 |@{fg shine}+-------------------------------------+@{fg fill}|
 |@{fg shine}|@{fg text}                  +-----------------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
 |@{fg shine}|@{fg text}             Name |                 |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <- Nome del file
 @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}                  +-----------------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
 |@{fg shine}|@{fg text}                  +-----------------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
 |@{fg shine}|@{fg text}           Author |                 |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <- Nome dell'autore
 @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}                  +-----------------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
 |@{fg shine}|@{fg text}                  +--------------++-+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
 |@{fg shine}|@{fg text} @{u}D@{uu}evice to expand |              ||@{fg shine}^@{fg text}|@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <- Device per la decompressione
 @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}                  +--------------++-+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
 |@{fg shine}|@{fg text}                  +-----------------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
 |@{fg shine}|@{fg text}             Date |                 |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <- Data di creazione
 @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}                  +-----------------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
 |@{fg shine}|@{fg text}                  +-----------------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
 |@{fg shine}|@{fg text}          Comment |                 |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <- Commento
 @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}                  +-----------------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
 |@{fg shine}+-------------------------------------+@{fg fill}|
 |@{fg shine}+-------------------------------------+@{fg fill}|
