 |@{fg shine}|@{fg text}|       @{u}O@{uu}k       | |     @{u}C@{uu}ancel     |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-
 @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}+----------------+ +----------------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}    Cancel = Anulla l'immissione
 @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-------------------------------------+@{fg fill}|
 +-------------------------------------+-+
